    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We previously found that type 2 immunity promotes COVID-19 pathogenesis in a mouse model. To test relevance to human disease we used electronic health record databases and determined that patients on dupilumab (anti-IL-4R\n                  <jats:italic>\u03b1</jats:italic>\n                  monoclonal antibody that blocks IL-13 and IL-4 signaling) at the time of COVID-19 infection had lower mortality.\n                </jats:p>",
